data.name: 0000 (538.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Come on Mikuru, let's hurry!

data.name: 0001 (538.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: But, w-we're not allowed to run in the corridor…

data.name: 0002 (538.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: The wonders of the world won't just sit still and wait for us!

data.name: 0003 (538.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: So hurry up!

data.name: 0004 (538.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Ehhh—

data.name: 0005 (538.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Um, I found this on the floor…

data.name: 0006 (538.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: What's this?

data.name: 0007 (538.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Umm, Kyon said it has computer data in it…

data.name: 0008 (538.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Computer data?

data.name: 0009 (538.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Hmm… Oh, it has Computer Research Society written on it?

data.name: 0010 (538.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Y-yes.

data.name: 0011 (538.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: It might be something really important, then, right?

data.name: 0012 (538.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: You're right. We'd better give it back to them…

data.name: 0013 (538.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: What are you talking about, Mikuru?!

data.name: 0014 (538.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: We obviously have to check what's inside first!

data.name: 0015 (538.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Huh?! Is that okay?

data.name: 0016 (538.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: As if I'd so easily give back such an interesting looking thing!

data.name: 0017 (538.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: I wonder what's on it.

data.name: 0018 (538.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Questionable images, maybe?

data.name: 0019 (538.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Or maybe—something like a dangerous computer virus?

data.name: 0020 (538.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Either way, we've gotten hold of a weakness of theirs!

data.name: 0021 (538.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Um, it might not have anything interesting inside, or it might be broken…

data.name: 0022 (538.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: I want to check right away, but first let's meet up with Koizumi and the others.
